{
  "stem": "7458.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Certainly, later on, we heard about Stalingrad and the horrible defeat that the Germans suffered at Stalingrad where some [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] whole army was surrounded and destroyed and cap-- captured by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So suddenly, there was a ray of hope, that if you could only, somehow, provide for hiding places, or make some arrangements, or survive maybe another year or two, maybe the Germans will be defeated, and maybe you'll have a chance to survive.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In order to prepare for that, my father and my older siblings, my brother, Meyer, who was, I don't know, maybe 16 years older than I, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and my brother, Maishe, who was fours years older than I, they begin to plan hiding places.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "First of all, we built a little hiding place above the house where every time they would come to round up a few healthy young Jews, my brothers would run up and hide.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But then we also built a very ingenious hiding place above the tannery.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I have a sketch that I drew of it, which I'm including in memoirs, which I'm writing right now.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and that sketch will show how we built a hiding place above the tannery.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll describe it when you're photographing it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there, we could hide about maybe 15 people for a-- on a temporary basis.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We figured, when liquidation comes, maybe we can run and hide there for a while until such time as we can leave Jasionowka altogether.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In addition, my father and my family negotiated with a farmer who lived in the forest.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this farmer said to us, if you'll give me all of your money and gold and leather and whatever you've got, I will give you shelter when liquidation comes.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
